[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":935},["ShallowReactive",2],{"content-/blog/2-my-vscode-setup":3,"content-authors":528,"content-query-qKssHOB7DJ":544},{"article":4,"surround":521},{"_path":5,"_dir":6,"_draft":7,"_partial":7,"_locale":8,"title":9,"description":10,"headline":11,"abstract":12,"date":13,"dateUpdated":8,"author":14,"authorUrl":15,"socialImage":16,"body":22,"_type":515,"_id":516,"_source":517,"_file":518,"_stem":519,"_extension":520},"/blog/2-my-vscode-setup","blog",false,"","My VSCode Setup | Blog","Explore my minimalist VSCode setup featuring the Minimal Mist theme and settings for a clean, distraction-free coding environment.","My VSCode Setup","Discover how the Minimal Mist theme and custom VSCode settings create a clean and focused coding environment.","2024-07-17T12:00:00","Muhammad Ubaid Raza","/",{"src":17,"mime":18,"alt":19,"width":20,"height":21},"/img/blog/2-my-vscode-setup/typescript-dark.png","png","Workplace Screenshot",1200,630,{"type":23,"children":24,"toc":502},"root",[25,33,39,48,55,62,76,82,87,93,98,104,109,115,120,125,131,136,143,152,158,171,468,491,496],{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":28,"children":30},"element","h1",{"id":29},"my-vscode-setup",[31],{"type":32,"value":11},"text",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":35,"children":36},"p",{},[37],{"type":32,"value":38},"Hello, fellow developers! I’m Muhammad Ubaid Raza, and I want to share my latest VSCode setup with you. I've crafted this environment to be as minimalist and distraction-free as possible, and I call it Minimal Mist. This theme and setup have greatly enhanced my coding experience, and I hope it can do the same for you.",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":40,"children":41},{},[42],{"type":26,"tag":43,"props":44,"children":45},"strong",{},[46],{"type":32,"value":47},"You can install this theme from VsCode marketplace: [Minimal Mist](Minimal Mist - Visual Studio Marketplace)",{"type":26,"tag":49,"props":50,"children":52},"h2",{"id":51},"features-of-minimal-mist",[53],{"type":32,"value":54},"Features of Minimal Mist",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":57,"children":59},"h3",{"id":58},"subtle-background",[60],{"type":32,"value":61},"Subtle Background",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":63,"children":64},{},[65,67,74],{"type":32,"value":66},"I chose a soft and soothing background color ",{"type":26,"tag":68,"props":69,"children":71},"code",{"className":70},[],[72],{"type":32,"value":73},"#f6f5f0",{"type":32,"value":75},". This subtle hue reduces eye strain and creates a calm coding environment, perfect for long coding sessions.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":77,"children":79},{"id":78},"shadow-free-design",[80],{"type":32,"value":81},"Shadow-Free Design",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":83,"children":84},{},[85],{"type":32,"value":86},"In my quest for a cleaner interface, I disabled shadows. This makes the interface feel lighter and less cluttered, allowing me to focus more on my code.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":88,"children":90},{"id":89},"streamlined-borders",[91],{"type":32,"value":92},"Streamlined Borders",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":94,"children":95},{},[96],{"type":32,"value":97},"Borders can often add unnecessary visual noise, so I simplified, minimized, or removed them. This provides a clean and focused workspace that helps keep distractions at bay.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":99,"children":101},{"id":100},"clean-look",[102],{"type":32,"value":103},"Clean Look",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":105,"children":106},{},[107],{"type":32,"value":108},"Overall, the goal is a refined, distraction-free interface that lets me concentrate on what matters most - the code.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":110,"children":112},{"id":111},"unified-design",[113],{"type":32,"value":114},"Unified Design",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":116,"children":117},{},[118],{"type":32,"value":119},"The dark theme maintains the same streamlined, shadow-free design and simplified borders for a cohesive look.",{"type":26,"tag":34,"props":121,"children":122},{},[123],{"type":32,"value":124},"Minimal Mist, both in ligh